I’M NOT FUQ’N LEAVING!!! 🗣️

The morning of Black Friday, my biggest @glamaholiclifestyle drop, my biggest campaign, my biggest investment in 13 years….Instagram decided to flag my page because of a story (not a post) of Santana opening his Christmas gifts in 2021 🫣

A “glitch” that they couldn’t figure out why or how it happened for 3 weeks. 🤔 

I didn’t get to go live on Black Friday for #TheGlamAholicShoppingExperience. I didn’t get to thank everyone for the birthday wishes. I couldn’t carry out and complete my Black Friday/ Cyber Monday campaign🥹

But TODAY we will #RedoBlackFriday!!! 🗣️

I miss y’all so much! I miss not being able to talk to y’all about what’s happening, what’s new and what’s next!! 😔

TODAY we will #RedoBlackFriday!! 🗣️

Today I’m gonna do something that I’ve never done before 🤞🏾 Today we will #RedoBlackFriday like never before! 

They can lock my account, but never my mind…you know I put it to work & can’t wait to make this up to y’all. God said “Rest. Reset”. AND DID 🙌🏾

Meet me on live at 3:30pm EST as we #REDOBLACKFRIDAY 🗣️ Repost and tag a friend to let them know I’MMMMMMM BACKKKKKKKKK!! I’m still hereeeeeee!!! 😝 

GLAM-AHOLICS ARE YOU WITH ME?! 🗣️ 
#GlamAholicLifestyle #TheGlamAholicShoppingExperience #REDOBLACKFRIDAY

Dear Instagram….

One thing you taught me in the last 3 weeks, is to never let someone have control over me + what I’ve built for the past 13 years. Say less 😎

The Mia Ray app coming 2023 🥳

But until then….the show must go on! I am so glad I got to #RedoBlackFriday with my Glam-Aholics today! I missed y’all so much! You can catch the replay in my reels/story. 🥰

Hopefully they’ll be a few Glam-Aholics nice enough to share in the comments the deals going on for today…they all end Midnight EST! 🔥 

#GlamAholicLifestyle

🎶Ain’t this what they been waiting for….🎶 😝

Y’all know I am always in the holiday spirit + I can’t wait to see y’all unwrap these! 🤶🏽

2. These will be available in store on Friday at the @GlamAholicLifestyle pop up shop (1020 Woodward Ave.) at 10am. Online 3pm EST www.GlamAholicLifestyle.com. 🥳

3. I can make no promises that these will arrive to you by Christmas. We will be working overtime to try our best to have them to you as soon as possible 🥰🤞🏾

I remember when I started @GlamAholicLifestyle I created a vision board of all my goals & dreams for my brand. One night Chrissy wrote on a pink sticky note “You will be successful!” and stuck it to my board. I still have that sticky note. She doesn’t know how much I needed that and how often I read that note as a reminder 🥹 

I remember going to the Southfield Public Library to work on my brand while she worked on her Master’s Degree in HR. I knew SHE would be successful because I never knew someone to LOVE Human Resources as much as she did…I used to laugh at her so much about it 😭 Now I’m so thankful that she does because she handles all my HR affairs like a G! 💪🏾

I met this woman when I was 10 years old…we’ll be 40 next year…not many people can say that they have THIS 🥹 I trust her with my business and with my life…for life ❤️🤞🏾

(And yes, we work well together lol Work is work and BFF time is separate 🥰) 

#GlamAholicLifestyle

The @cdkkreations team was such a pleasure to work with…seamless from beginning to end & now she is stuck with me for life! 😌🤣 

She really turned my vision into reality 🤩 It was the sequin bell bottoms, detachable train + cheerleaders for me 😝 I loved both looks & felt so comfortable 🥰 

(Excuse my hair…I’d just taken my braids out the night before the fitting…y’all say yall like to see the real  so here it is. The grind ain’t always pretty 🤷🏽‍♀️🤣)

“From now on…don’t nobody talk to me directly! You got business with me, you talk to Huey! Huey, you talk to me! 🗣️”

This is my Huey 😎 If you’re trying to get to me….you have to get through Ms. Monyai first! I tell ppl weekly how I wish that I could clone her 🥹 I had admired her for years on IG…she always had the best recipes, organizational tips & home decor. She was my spirit animal (but she’s wayyyyy nicer than me 🤣) 

I love getting to see her creativity and ideas unfold up close & personal at @glamaholiclifestyle! 🤩

She is responsible for the layouts of our pop up shops + our gorgeous warehouse. Every paint color, neon/street sign, desk….even down to our infamous pink toilet paper, she’s responsible for it 🦸🏽‍♀️

Her level of patience & kindness is unreal 🥹 I know that I will not have Monyai for long. Her star shines so bright and I can’t wait for the world to see it! 🤩 @HGTV👏🏽 MY 👏🏽 GIRL 👏🏽

#GlamAholicLifestyle #HappyWomensHistoryMonth

I don’t think either of us saw THIS in our future, but if “I meant what I said.” was a person….her name would be Blair 🤞🏾💪🏾❤️

At the close of Cyber Monday, this was the amount of orders that @glamaholiclifestyle had received thus far in the month of November, with 23,238 of them happening over the weekend 🥳

With that being said, today is November 30th…the 5th business day of shipping and the amount of unpleasant comments, DMs, emails and now chargebacks after only 5 days is very disheartening. But as most of you have always witnessed…my new level unlocks right here before your eyes 🎮

In 13 years, I have never stolen from a customer. I have never purposely not shipped an order. I have 2 warehouses totaling over 30,000 sq ft overflowing with inventory. I promise, I am not trying to keep anyone’s order…I’m actually trying to hurry and make room for my new 2024 inventory 🫣

I’ll be completely honest (as always lol) and say that I was not prepared for over 20,000 orders in a few days. I have not stopped working, moving, shipping or strategizing on how to conquer yet another learning curve and of course my hiccup is of no fault to anyone that made a purchase during this time. It is not fair to you if you feel that this is a delay and/or if you feel you may experience one. I take full responsibility for not being prepared ❤️

If you prefer to not wait for your order, I completely understand! We can cancel the order upon your request, by clicking the Email button in my bio (please remember to include your Name + Order Number 🙏🏽). 

Unfortunately, there are only 2 options. Accept the refund of your order and/or patiently wait for your order to arrive in 14 BUSINESS days (refraining from commenting and emailing about an update because your order is actually on the way 🤞🏾). If you decide to wait for your order, just know that your patience is GREATLY appreciated and my team & I are working around the clock to get these orders to you ASAP! ❤️📦💨

(Even my own father is waiting on his order ❤️) 

Pray for ya girl! 🥹😘
